<?xml version="1.0" encoding="UTF-8"?><song><title>ạ̹dẖạ gẖạbt ạlsẖms kẖlf ạlgẖywm</title>
<lyrics>[V1]
 ạ̹dẖạ gẖābt ạlsẖãmsu kẖlfa ạlgẖywm̊
 wạ̉ḍḥy̱ ạlnãhāru kalyliⁿ ṭawyl̊
 wạ̹n gẖaṭãt̊ ạlsuḥ̊bu nwra ạlnjwm̊
 wqul̊ta fy ḍyqika ạảyna ạlsbyl̊

[C1]
   halumã.. halumã ḍʿyfa ạlfw̉ạd̊
   fanwru ạlrjạʾi yaʿum ạlʿbạd̊
   wkulũ ṭryqiⁿ mryriⁿ trạh̊
   sayuf̊ḍī binaf̊sika naḥ̊wa ạlḥayāh̊

[V2]
 wạ̹n̊ kun̊ta taq̊ḍy ṭiwạla ạlsnyn̊
 tjwb bnfsk ʿrḍ ạlqfạr̊
 wtasʿay̱ wtasʿay̱ bqlbiⁿ ḥazyn̊
 lạ̉nk tab̊gẖy̱ saryʿa ạltẖmạr̊

[V3]
 taʿāla wa qif̊ taḥ̊ta naj̊mi ạlsãmạʾ̊
 ffy ạlsẖrqi dẖā qd̊ badā mursẖdaⁿạ
 wsir̊ fy ạlṭãryqi ʿalaẙ̱ had̊yihi
 hunāka yswʿu hunāka ạlhdẙ̱

[V4]
 symlạ̉ qlbk nwr ạlmsyḥ
 wyhdạ̉ rwʿuk ạ̹dẖ tstryḥ
 ffy jnbh qd trknạ ạljrạḥ
 wmn qlbh fạḍ ḥb ṣryḥ</lyrics>
<aka>ạ̹dẖạ gẖạbt ạlsẖms</aka>
